Module kivakit.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.messaging.messages

Class Result<T>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.messaging.messages.Result<T>
public class Result<T> extends Object
A return value that contains an object OR a Message indicating that something went wrong. Success messages should not be returned with this object as the failed() method only tests for the existence of any message.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
